299
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没有什么做不到的</font>

300
00:16:25,710 --> 00:16:26,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（是吗？）</font>

301
00:16:26,130 --> 00:16:26,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（总觉得）</font>

302
00:16:26,500 --> 00:16:26,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（很可疑）</font>

303
00:16:31,260 --> 00:16:33,470
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好  就用这个鸟居好了</font>

304
00:16:38,660 --> 00:16:40,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">支配混沌的赤色黑暗啊</font>

305
00:16:41,530 --> 00:16:45,000
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">速速召来操纵时间流动之球</font>

306
00:16:45,450 --> 00:16:48,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不断重复巡回的终焉之灯火</font>

307
00:16:49,000 --> 00:16:51,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">让此起彼伏的雷声占据天空</font>

308
00:16:51,700 --> 00:16:54,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">迷走于黑暗之物  徘徊于阴霾之物</font>

309
00:16:54,570 --> 00:16:58,280
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">以汝等罪恶之名  化身为搬运时间之物吧</font>

310
00:16:58,950 --> 00:16:59,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（真是大吃一惊！）</font>

311
00:17:00,080 --> 00:17:00,660
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（应该说好怀念！）</font>

312
00:17:01,040 --> 00:17:01,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（现在已经没人会这么说了吧！）</font>

313
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:02,710
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（这是二十多年前的艺术风格吧！？）</font>

314
00:17:24,810 --> 00:17:24,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（被那种恶心感吓退了一步）</font>

315
00:17:24,980 --> 00:17:25,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（连心也揪了起来）</font>

316
00:17:25,110 --> 00:17:25,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（差点就要失去自我）</font>

317
00:17:25,500 --> 00:17:28,480
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">怎么回事  这东西连接到异次元了吗</font>

318
00:17:28,690 --> 00:17:29,620
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  就是这样</font>

319
00:17:30,050 --> 00:17:32,650
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我还是第一次做这个东西  不过还不错的样子</font>

320
00:17:32,820 --> 00:17:35,530
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">虽说变成幼女力量基本消失</font>

321
00:17:35,610 --> 00:17:36,870
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但吾还真是名不虚传啊</font>

322
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:40,970
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可话不是那么说吧  既然还有力量生成异次元</font>

323
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:43,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">又怎么能说是力量消失了呢</font>

324
00:17:43,680 --> 00:17:46,380
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这不是吾的力量  而是这灵场的力量</font>

325
00:17:47,000 --> 00:17:49,540
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">就像那让人不愉快的夏威夷衫小鬼所说的</font>

326
00:17:49,640 --> 00:17:56,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">把聚集而来的怪异能量简单转化为热能而已</font>

327
00:17:56,360 --> 00:17:57,840
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">搞什么嘛  简直是伪科学</font>

328
00:17:58,340 --> 00:18:00,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说我们得快点哦</font>

329
00:18:00,460 --> 00:18:02,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这门大概没法再开一次了</font>

330
00:18:03,170 --> 00:18:05,360
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">再过一分钟应该就会关上</font>

331
00:18:05,530 --> 00:18:08,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">一分钟？稍等一下  我还没做好心理准备</font>

332
00:18:09,280 --> 00:18:11,960
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不用做准备  只是简单跳进去就好了</font>

333
00:18:12,300 --> 00:18:14,050
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎？这么简单就行？</font>

334
00:18:14,360 --> 00:18:18,680
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">没那么多需要准备的  不过是时间移动而已嘛</font>

335
00:18:21,490 --> 00:18:22,330
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（总觉得，忍说得十分轻松）</font>

336
00:18:22,330 --> 00:18:22,750
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（因为她说得十分轻松）</font>

337
00:18:22,750 --> 00:18:23,500
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（感觉危险性应该…会很低的）</font>

338
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">OK  那我们走吧</font>

339
00:18:26,280 --> 00:18:27,980
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哦  出发了</font>

340
00:18:28,970 --> 00:18:30,300
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  对了汝啊</font>

341
00:18:30,740 --> 00:18:31,340
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">什么事？</font>

342
00:18:31,850 --> 00:18:33,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯  那块表</font>

343
00:18:33,450 --> 00:18:33,820
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊？</font>

344
00:18:34,100 --> 00:18:35,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那块手表</font>

345
00:18:35,570 --> 00:18:40,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">明明不是左撇子却为拉风故意戴在右手的汝的手表</font>

346
00:18:41,140 --> 00:18:42,100
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">借给吾用用</font>

347
00:18:42,280 --> 00:18:44,640
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不用那么详细说明我也能明白好么</font>

348
00:18:45,130 --> 00:18:46,570
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">嗯？但为什么要手表</font>

349
00:18:46,650 --> 00:18:47,420
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">听话</font>

350
00:18:53,660 --> 00:18:54,860
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">发什么呆啊</font>

351
00:19:00,860 --> 00:19:03,600
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说  不要为这种事激动好不好</font>

352
00:19:03,810 --> 00:19:05,610
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">上厕所在一起  洗澡也在一起</font>

353
00:19:05,720 --> 00:19:08,130
