354
00:19:08,200 --> 00:19:10,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊不…但是和异性牵手这种事</font>

355
00:19:10,940 --> 00:19:14,450
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">对我这好少年来说可是值得激动一辈子的事啊</font>

356
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:15,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">麻烦死了</font>

357
00:19:15,290 --> 00:19:16,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好了 快点往里面跳</font>

358
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:21,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾的时间观念很淡薄  只能靠你引导了</font>

359
00:19:22,050 --> 00:19:24,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊  这样啊  原来如此</font>

360
00:19:24,240 --> 00:19:25,270
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">你一个人做不到啊</font>

361
00:19:26,680 --> 00:19:29,040
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">好吧  那我就带你出发吧  小忍</font>

362
00:19:29,580 --> 00:19:30,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">向着未知的世界！</font>

363
00:19:32,020 --> 00:19:32,520
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（只要一穿过鸟居）</font>

364
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:33,020
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（就能回到昨天这种好事我从没想过）</font>

365
00:19:33,020 --> 00:19:33,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（应该说我在想的都是八九寺的事）</font>

366
00:19:34,080 --> 00:19:36,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">喂  汝啊  快醒过来</font>

367
00:19:36,450 --> 00:19:38,690
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">不要被这种程度的撞击搞晕好不好</font>

368
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,250
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那个…</font>

369
00:19:44,450 --> 00:19:45,940
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">咦？现在几点</font>

370
00:19:46,320 --> 00:19:47,830
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">十二点  正中午</font>

371
00:19:51,080 --> 00:19:53,460
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这里是半山腰附近吗</font>

372
00:19:56,800 --> 00:19:59,580
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">话说  时间移动真的成功了吗</font>

373
00:19:59,740 --> 00:20:01,800
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">那当然是成功了</font>

374
00:20:03,380 --> 00:20:06,140
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">吾从生下来就未曾失败过</font>

375
00:20:06,580 --> 00:20:08,880
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我说你说大话也不脸红啊</font>

376
00:20:09,580 --> 00:20:14,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">但是说起来8月19日好像确实是这样的晴天</font>

377
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">可话说回来  该不是只是从阶梯摔下来</font>

378
00:20:17,050 --> 00:20:19,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">单纯昏迷了12个小时而已吧</font>

379
00:20:19,700 --> 00:20:19,780
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（那可就麻烦了）</font>

380
00:20:19,780 --> 00:20:19,900
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（不但作业没做，就连开学典礼也翘掉了）</font>

381
00:20:19,900 --> 00:20:20,110
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="33">{\an8}（会被羽川杀掉的…）</font>

382
00:20:23,250 --> 00:20:24,180
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我说  小忍</font>

383
00:20:24,410 --> 00:20:25,090
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">什么事</font>

384
00:20:25,610 --> 00:20:27,930
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">回去时也从那个鸟居回去就可以了吗</font>

385
00:20:28,240 --> 00:20:31,370
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">啊？啊…差不多啦</font>

386
00:20:31,610 --> 00:20:33,130
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">为什么回答地一点也不干脆</font>

387
00:20:33,340 --> 00:20:37,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个…其实我还没怎么想过回去的方法</font>

388
00:20:38,460 --> 00:20:44,240
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">说起来  打开时间之门的并不是小忍自身的力量</font>

389
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:48,560
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">而是利用北白蛇神社这一聚积点的灵场力量</font>

390
00:20:49,850 --> 00:20:55,400
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">既然我们已经消耗掉了那种力量  那门岂不是再也打不开了？</font>

391
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:57,230
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">这个…</font>

392
00:20:57,500 --> 00:20:59,120
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">喂  给我等等小忍</font>

393
00:20:59,440 --> 00:21:04,210
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">我们现在该不会陷入无法从昨天的世界回到原来世界的境地了吧</font>

394
00:21:04,320 --> 00:21:07,220
<font face="FZZhunYuan-M02" size="45">哎呀  没事没事  吾之主人</font>

395
